{"tid":1857012,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣國防部緊急受命 派兵支援口罩生產","createTime":"2020-02-02T03:31:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T04:43:49.000Z","uid":323443,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"c570d8c9fdeb9d394becc52d21f50ad6958d21ac","tid":1857012,"uid":323443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T03:31:56.000Z","msg":"口罩大缺貨引發民怨，國防部上午接獲中央流行疫情指揮中心指示，要求派兵前往口罩工廠生產線協助生產口罩。國軍緊急調兵遣將，完成這項任務。<br />\n<br />\n行政院已拍板以<span style=\"color: red;\">最快速度新建62條口罩產線，包括10%兒童口罩模具</span>，現已盤點完畢機器放置與生產空間，並委託國內口罩專業生產工廠協助製造。3日起開始的一個月內，62條產線會陸續上線，產能可從目前的每日400萬片逐步提高至<span style=\"color: red;\">每日1000萬片</span>，讓國內供應更穩定。<br />\n<br />\n而經濟部規劃新建62條口罩產線，將在3日起的一個月內陸續上線，人力不足部分洽請國防部支援；國防部上午受命檢討兵力，計畫全力滿足生產線人力需求。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/10930/4316609\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F10930%2F4316609&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9Ag0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=edcc7443\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/10930/4316609</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n口罩大作戰！"},{"pid":"0d31a95137f141b87c893bc76e0d8693fa900aeb","tid":1857012,"uid":33848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T03:32:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab8e795f4cbb3a503238d089443c5856745a04a","tid":1857012,"uid":140742,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T03:33:25.000Z","msg":"駐港解放軍仲摺被？"},{"pid":"49703f0256af6718af8d58933da3544f4512125c","tid":1857012,"uid":127929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T03:33:38.000Z","msg":"Taiwan no.1<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/